fields.calculatedFormula:
grax__Records_To_Process__c = 0 &&
(
  grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__c = null && grax__Execution_Unique_Key__c = null && grax__of_Times_Sent__c >= 24 ||
  grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__c = null && grax__Execution_Unique_Key__c != null || 
  ( 
    NOT(ISPICKVAL(grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__type__c, 'Hierarchy')) ||
    NOT(grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__Progressive__c)
  ) &&
  (
    (
      NOT(grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__Is_Running__c) &&
      DATEVALUE(CreatedDate) < TODAY() - 15
    ) ||
    (
      grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__Execution_Unique_Key__c != grax__Execution_Unique_Key__c &&
      NOT(grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__Is_Running__c)
    ) ||
    (
      grax__Records_Failed_to_Delete__c = 0 &&
      grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__Can_Delete_GRAX_Records__c &&
      (
        ISPICKVAL(grax__Status__c, 'Sent Successful') ||
        (
          ISPICKVAL(grax__Status__c, 'Not Sent') &&
          NOT(grax__GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.grax__Is_Running__c)
        )
      ) && 
      (
         ISBLANK(grax__GRAX_Archive_Process__c) || 
         grax__GRAX_Archive_Process__r.grax__Can_Delete_GRAX_Record__c
      )
    )
  )
)
fields.label: Can Delete GRAX Record?
fields.name: grax__Can_Delete_GRAX_Record__c
